## kamel-admin-sam

SAM stack for the Admin backend API.

### What this stack owns

- One HTTP API for admin routes
- Five Lambda functions:
  - `bikes-handler`
  - `users-handler`
  - `providers-handler`
  - `service-centres-handler`
  - `dashboard-handler`
- One per-stack JWT authorizer config tied to the shared Cognito user pool and admin app client

### Shared dependencies

This stack imports shared values from:

- `aws-kamel-network`
  - Lambda security group
  - private subnet IDs
- `aws-kamel-auth`
  - user pool ID
  - user pool ARN
  - issuer URL
  - admin app client ID

### Deployment

```powershell
sam build --config-env dev
sam deploy --config-env dev
```
